quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,171,aur jab hum ne un ( ke suron ) par pahar utha kharakiya goya woh saibaan tha aur unhon ne khayaalkiya ke woh un par girta hai to ( hum ne kaha ke ) jo hum ne tumhe diya hai usay zor se pakdae raho. aur jo is mein likha hai is par amal karo taakay bach jao
  7,172,aur jab tumahray perwar-digaar ne bani aadam se yani un ki pithon se un ki aulaad nikaali to un se khud un ke muqablay mein iqraar kara liya ( yani un se poocha ke )kiya tumhara perwar-digaar nahi hon. woh kehnay lagey kyun nahi hum gawah hain ( ke to hamara perwar-digaar hai ). yeh iqraar is liye karaya tha ke qayamat ke din ( kahin yun nah ) kehnay lagu ke hum ko to is ki khabar hi nah thi
  7,173,ya yeh ( nah ) kaho ke shirk to pehlay hamaray barron nekiya tha. aur hum to un ki aulaad they ( jo ) un ke baad ( peda hue ). tokiya jo kaam ahal baatil karte rahay is ke badlay to hamein halaak karta hai
  7,174,aur isi terhan hum ( apni ) ayatain khol khol kar bayan karte hain taakay yeh rujoo karen
  7,175,aur un ko is shakhs ka haal parh kar suna do jis ko hum ne apni ayatain ataa farmaen ( aur haft parcha ٴ ilm shar'aa )se muzayyankiya ) to is ne un ko utaar diya phir shetan is ke peechay laga to woh gumrahon mein hogaya
  7,176,aur agar hum chahtay to un ayaton se is ( ke darjay ) ko buland kar dete magar woh to pasti ki taraf mael hogaya aur apni khwahish ke peechay chal para. to is ki misaal kuttay ki si hogayi ke agar sakhti karo to zabaan nikalay rahay aur yuhin chore do to bhi zabaan nikalay rahay. yahi misaal un logon ki hai jinhon ne hamari ayaton ko jhatlaya to un se yeh qissa bayan kardo. taakay woh fikar karen
  7,177,jin logon ne hamari ayaton ki takzieeb ki un ki misaal buri hai aur unhon ne nuqsaan (kiya to ) apna hikiya
  7,178,jis ko khuda hadaayat day wohi raah yab hai aur jis ko gumraah kere to aisay hi log nuqsaan uthany walay hain
